data.name: ReadCaseCaseAssignmentOfficeOfficeServiceProvider
data.value: select T2.CAS_NO, T2.REASON_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SPD_ID, T2.OFF_ID, T2.OSP_CODE, T2.OSP_DATE, T3.OFFICE_ID, T3.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T3.OFFICE_ID >= @officeId1) and ( (T3.OFFICE_ID > @officeId1) or ( (T3.OFFICE_ID = @officeId1) and (T2.SPD_ID >= @spdId) and ( (T2.SPD_ID > @spdId) or ( (T2.SPD_ID = @spdId) and (T2.CAS_NO > @casNo) ) ) ) ) and (T3.OFFICE_ID = T2.OFF_ID) and (T2.REASON_CODE = 'RSP') and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T3.OFFICE_ID between cast(@officeId2 as smallint) and cast(@officeId3 as smallint)) order by T3.OFFICE_ID, T2.SPD_ID, T2.CAS_NO
